_sText:
Got bored and was trying to make a longer map with multiple route potential but I decided to stop at 1:30ish because it felt like the right time to end it, this is a theme/design I wanted to do for a while and it turned out okay even though it was only in the works for a day. I tried at least adding a few routes and I quite enjoy playing it, also has a 35 sec bonus which is pretty fun imo.


Here's a slow and bad run just to show it a bit better than the screenshots, put it together quickly so sorry that it's not an impressive run or anything.
